sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as RHOAI Operator<br/>controller-manager
    participant GitRepo as Git Repository<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>User Workload Monitoring
    participant Kubelet as Kubelet

    %% Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation
    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over Admin,Operator: Flow 1: DataScienceCluster Creation
        Admin->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply -f datasciencecluster.yaml<br/>User credentials
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification (in-memory)<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: DSCInitialization spec

        opt Custom manifests configured
            Operator->>GitRepo: GET /tarball/branch<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>No auth
            GitRepo-->>Operator: Manifest tarball
        end

        Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE Deployments, Services, Routes<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Resources created

        Operator->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DataScienceCluster status<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Admin: Status: Ready
    end

    %% Flow 2: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Prometheus,Operator: Flow 2: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>RBACProxy: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount JWT)
        RBACProxy->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/authentication.k8s.io/v1/tokenreviews<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>RBACProxy: Token valid: true
        RBACProxy->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>No auth (proxied)
        Operator-->>RBACProxy: Prometheus metrics
        RBACProxy-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
    end

    %% Flow 3: Health Monitoring
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Kubelet,Operator: Flow 3: Health Monitoring
        Kubelet->>Operator: GET /healthz<br/>HTTP/8081<br/>No auth
        Operator-->>Kubelet: 200 OK
        Kubelet->>Operator: GET /readyz<br/>HTTP/8081<br/>No auth
        Operator-->>Kubelet: 200 OK
    end

    %% Flow 4: Secret Generation
    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 4: OAuth Secret Generation
        Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret with annotation<br/>secret-generator.opendatahub.io/enabled<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch notification (SecretGenerator)<br/>In-memory
        Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE generated Secret<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Operator->>K8sAPI: UPDATE OAuthClient<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: OAuthClient updated
    end
